import { Drawer, List, ListItemText } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const DrawerComp = () => {
  return (
    <React.Fragment>
        <Drawer open={true}>
            <List>
                <ListItemText>
                    Login
                </ListItemText>
            </List>
        </Drawer>
    </React.Fragment>
  )
}

export default DrawerComp
